  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A right circular cylinder has a height of <math alttext=\"8 meters left parenthesis m right parenthesis\"><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>meters</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><mfenced><mtext>m</mtext></mfenced></math> and a base with a radius of <math alttext=\"12 m\"><mrow><mn>12</mn></mrow><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>m</mtext></math>. What is the volume, <math alttext=\"in m cubed\"><mtext>in</mtext><mo>&#160;</mo><msup><mtext>m</mtext><mn>3</mn></msup></math>, of the cylinder?</p>",
